571101.activity_medal_desc: The exacting leader of the Iron Blood Resistance. "I am always watching you."

571102.activity_medal_desc: A mysterious entity that appeared from beyond the stars. Its true nature is still unknown.

571103.activity_medal_desc: On the night the Star Beast descended, the cosmos shone more radiantly than ever before.

571104.activity_medal_desc: Strange tissue collected from the remains of an extradimensional beast. Classification: Scientific research material. Do not eat.

571105.activity_medal_desc: The Resistance's HQ, protected by a Mirror Sea and Eternal Star. Not exactly an ideal getaway resort, but it IS well-defended.

571106.activity_medal_desc: The extradimensional beasts are mighty, but our preparations are even mightier. As long as we survive this turbulent night, we shall walk proudly into hope's light.

576901.activity_medal_desc: "Late-spring reflected in embroidered silk, resplendent as golden peacock and silver qilin."

576902.activity_medal_desc: "The geese call, the first rays of dawn come. If you wish to marry me, do so before the ice melts."

576903.activity_medal_desc: "Poems, I compose beneath nights moonlit and snowy; paintings, I compose beneath clouds rainy and hazy."

576904.activity_medal_desc: "By three times does the plum blossom lack snow's pure white, yet the latter hath not a single portion of the former's fragrance."
576904.activity_medal_name: Sticker: Plum Blossoms in the Snow

576905.activity_medal_desc: Great adventures are all about the passion and flair!

576906.activity_medal_desc: "I sit at water's edge, watching the ever-changing clouds rise."

576907.activity_medal_desc: "As lotus roots grow in pairs, too lengthy are the ties between us."

576908.activity_medal_desc: Plan to topple the dastardly supervillain Chien Wu (crossed out) and celebrate the New Year!

581201.activity_medal_desc: "Sardegnia, the eternal land. As long as God's light shines over us, we shall forever be prosperous."

581202.activity_medal_desc: It is the power of faith that connects us all.

581203.activity_medal_desc: That is a Gazer. If you can see it, it can see you.

581204.activity_medal_desc: "Drawing is my favorite thing in the world!"

581205.activity_medal_desc: Second by second, the time ticks away. When, oh when, will we break free of our cage?
